maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday afternoon’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 3 Day” game were:
0-0-5, Wild: 6
(zero, zero, five; Wild: six)
